stanfordlogic.knowledge
Class GameInformation

java.lang.Object
  stanfordlogic.knowledge.GameInformation

public class GameInformation
extends java.lang.Object

Information we've extracted from the game description regarding structural, syntactical and other features of a game.

Note that the init facts are not in the static facts.

Author:
Based on code by Team Camembert: David Haley, Pierre-Yves Laligand
